* BrightBlade looked over the scimatics of the Cybertronien Fire, every deck

She had gathered over two storage programs full of imformation on this 
battle ship, all of it ready to be downloaded into the Predacon hard-drive.
With a snicker she opened her com-link and diverted it onto a coded 
frequincy. It was time to let her Predacons into the game.*

" Predacon base, this is BrightBlade. All information of the Maximal ship is 
ready to be downloaded. Instruct me when you are ready to recieve it."

* With that she looked at the screen again, the smile on her face growing
